  <name>Amphora</name>
  <summary>Listen to Pandora Internet Radio</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Amphora is a modern libadwaita client for Pandora Internet Radio, built
      in the spirit of Pithos. It streams your stations, shows album art and
      track information, and lets you rate songs to tune your stations.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Adaptive GTK4 / libadwaita interface</li>
      <li>Station switching and playback controls</li>
      <li>Love, ban and "tired of this song" feedback</li>
      <li>Selectable audio quality</li>
      <li>Credentials stored securely in the system keyring</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  <launchable type="desktop-id">net.kndy.Amphora.desktop</launchable>
